name: Hopper
description:
Hoppers NFTs are 10,000 randomly generated unique NFTs with on-chain
Attributes that will be used in Hoppers Game. The Hoppers themselves
were created by yellowbrah (@dirty_slogan) with over 120 hand-drawn
assets with a variety of skins, backgrounds, and features, Hoppers are
as beautiful as they are useful! There will be 5 tiers of rarity ranging
from Common to Legendary. Artistically, all 10,000 NFTs will be randomly
generated and unique.
